This image bundles wyoming_kokoro.py, a Python runtime for running Kokoro TTS
behind the Wyoming protocol, authored by Luca Chiabrera and distributed under
the MIT License (see LICENSE). Source:

    https://github.com/chiabre/wyoming-kokoro

Model files (Kokoro-ONNX) are not bundled; they are downloaded on first
container start from:

    https://github.com/thewh1teagle/kokoro-onnx

Kokoro-ONNX is distributed under the Apache-2.0 License.
